8:1c4|//!   bootstrap node when none is reachable.
9:0bd|//!
10:7b5|//! This module is parametric over room types: game-specific message types
11:14a|//! live in the game's own crates. Bootstrap nodes subscribe to the extra
12:c56|//! topics listed in [`NetworkManagerConfig::bootstrap_topics`] at the *raw*
13:6c5|//! gossip layer only — they never decode the traffic, they just have to be
14:656|//! subscribed, because iroh-gossip can only bootstrap a topic swarm through
15:22c|//! peers that are themselves subscribed to that topic.
